*Beautiiiiful SubhanAllah*
I started memorize Asma-ul-Husna two months ago and how much i was happy can't express in words when i saw "Asma-ul-Husna in Atif Aslam voice by Cokestudio😳😍" on my youtube home.

*Hadith:*
Abu Huraira reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, “Allah has ninety-nine names and whoever preserves them will enter Paradise.”
 
*Quranic Reference:*
 “And (all) the Most Beautiful Names belong to Allah, so call on Him by them" [al-A‘raaf 7:180].
